A well deserved World Title Number 3 for high-flying @gabrielmedina.
Relive history during the #ripcurlwslfinals on worldsurfleague.com. @ripcurl_usa

A big thank you and obrigado to all the fans out there. Without you, none of this is possible. @rissmoore10 @gabrielmedina
Relive history during the #ripcurlwslfinals, link in bio. @ripcurl_usa
